1810 POKE SB + 0,0:POKE SB + 1,8:REM  V1 FREQ
1820 POKE SB + 4,129:REM  NOISE + GATE
1830 PAUSE 0.08
1840 POKE SB + 1,3:REM  DROP FREQ
1850 PAUSE 0.08
1860 POKE SB + 4,128:REM  GATE OFF
1870 RETURN
1880 RETURN
