1910 POKE SB + 1,15:POKE SB + 4,65:PAUSE 0.05:REM  PULSE + GATE
1920 POKE SB + 1,20:PAUSE 0.05
1930 POKE SB + 1,25:PAUSE 0.05
1940 POKE SB + 4,64:REM  GATE OFF
1950 RETURN
2000 REM   --- SFX LEVEL UP ---
2001 POKE SB + 10,2:POKE SB + 11,12
2002 POKE SB + 13,9:POKE SB + 14,128
2003 POKE 8000,1:POKE 8001,55:POKE 8002,8:POKE 8003,12
2004 POKE 8004,1:POKE 8005,60:POKE 8006,8:POKE 8007,12
2005 POKE 8008,1:POKE 8009,64:POKE 8010,8:POKE 8011,12
2006 POKE 8012,255
2007 POKE SB + 32,64:POKE SB + 33,31
2008 POKE SB + 35,80
2009 POKE SB + 34,1
