2020 POKE SB + 1,22:PAUSE 0.05:REM  C NOTE
2030 POKE SB + 1,28:PAUSE 0.1:REM  E NOTE
2040 POKE SB + 4,64:REM  GATE OFF
2050 RETURN
2100 REM   --- SFX GAME OVER ---
2101 POKE SB + 4,0:PAUSE 0.05
2110 POKE SB + 1,15:POKE SB + 4,33:REM  SAW + GATE
2120 PAUSE 0.15
2130 POKE SB + 1,10:PAUSE 0.15
2140 POKE SB + 1,5:PAUSE 0.15
2150 POKE SB + 4,32:REM  GATE OFF
2160 RETURN
